rows.label: qst400206_msg0001
rows.name:
Ahh, sorry...
I'm only really interested in plants.
I don't keep up with the latest rumors...

rows.label: qst400206_msg0002
rows.name:
I want to become a botanist in
Superbia, but my parents keep
saying it's too dangerous...

rows.label: qst400206_msg0003
rows.name:
It's been a whole decade now
since Superbia and Invidia
ceased hostilities...

rows.label: qst400206_msg0004
rows.name:
And sure, there's been this nasty
group called Iira popping up in
the news lately, but still...

rows.label: qst400206_msg0005
rows.name:
It's not like anything bad's gonna
happen where Superbia's in charge.
Doesn't this peaceful town prove that?
